.1％學生回答讀書時間為0，比2017年升4個百分點。文科生佔48.6％，理科為54.5％。有打工的學生，回答讀書時間為0的為54.5％。沒有打工的學生為49.4％。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2df36b820f67aee84ef7c859d73ee8713cad5fd0","tid":2494014,"uid":170399,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"咁你開返個一齊討論學術書<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cb7e856de4821bbcf0f3f0d34e29a7eaade649","tid":2494014,"uid":233118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"讀書要用腦<br />\n用腦其實好攰 某程度比得上做運動<br />\n尤其係讀學術書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文青書都係啲消遣讀物 內容又千遍一律  又係潮流產物 自然多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e889f1e92fc75db359c63fc0198cb54ffaa5a6","tid":2494014,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23cb7e856de4821bbcf0f3f0d34e29a7eaade649","tid":2494014,"uid":233118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"讀書要用腦<br />\n用腦其實好攰 某程度比得上做運動<br />\n尤其係讀學術書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文青書都係啲消遣讀物 內容又千遍一律  又係潮流產物 自然多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"內容點千篇一律法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b0c227709a2a263e96415ce2ed7718167f5292","tid":2494014,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e889f1e92fc75db359c63fc0198cb54ffaa5a6","tid":2494014,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23cb7e856de4821bbcf0f3f0d34e29a7eaade649","tid":2494014,"uid":233118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"讀書要用腦<br />\n用腦其實好攰 某程度比得上做運動<br />\n尤其係讀學術書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文青書都係啲消遣讀物 內容又千遍一律  又係潮流產物 自然多人睇<img src=\"/asse